snippet.title: Terra Swoop Force (Remastered) - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:

GDL has assembled an elite elytra task force for a top-secret, high-risk mission. Step into your Thermal Flight Armor; it’s time to begin the flight of your life!

Your journey to the center of the earth is just the beginning of the adventure! Search “GDL” on the Minecraft Marketplace to experience more of the story.

! Singleplayer/multiplayer
! Free download
